Akismet plugin for lokka

(1) Obtain your Akismet account and API KEY at http://akismet.com/ now.
(2) Put lokka-akismet directory in $LOKKA_HOME/public/plugins
(3) Restart lokka and login to admin page.
(4) Open plugins page and select Akismet.
(5) Type your Akismet API Key solemnly and save.
(6) Sing a eulogy on spammers.
